break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Syntax：948 - Zed 已准备好用于生产</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Wes 和 Scott 深入分析了炙手可热的 Rust 编写的编辑器 Zed——它的速度、美观性，以及为何终于可以用于生产。从 Git UI 到扩展市场和 AI 工具，他们分析了 Zed 的亮点、缺失功能，以及是否该放弃 VS Code。讨论了 Zed 的 UI 设计、编辑器体验、扩展生态系统、Git 界面、问题诊断 UI、实时协作、命令行技巧、AI 集成等功能。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://syntax.fm/948\" target=\"_blank\">https://syntax.fm/948</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-w